5
00:01:54,229 --> 00:01:56,070
is Turtle Hill.

6
00:01:56,720 --> 00:01:57,770
Here

7
00:01:57,979 --> 00:02:00,290
not only has my bones and blood,

8
00:02:00,590 --> 00:02:03,150
but also this heavenly stone.

9
00:02:04,560 --> 00:02:06,880
My husband told me

10
00:02:07,480 --> 00:02:12,030
this ox figure is
a rare stone from heaven.

11
00:02:12,350 --> 00:02:14,920
It sits here silently,

12
00:02:15,220 --> 00:02:16,590
guarding

13
00:02:16,610 --> 00:02:18,560
Ox Temple Village.

14
00:02:19,520 --> 00:02:22,280
Time flies.

15
00:02:22,520 --> 00:02:24,040
In the blink of an eye,

16
00:02:24,210 --> 00:02:26,610
more than 50 years have passed.

17
00:02:27,630 --> 00:02:28,760
But I

18
00:02:28,970 --> 00:02:31,730
still often think of

19
00:02:32,110 --> 00:02:35,040
the year that changed my life.

20
00:02:34,050 --> 00:02:43,190
[December 8, 1926; Solar term: Major Snow]
[Ox Temple Village, Shandong]

21
00:02:35,470 --> 00:02:39,430
It was the 4th day of winter in
the 15th year of Republic of China.

22
00:02:40,190 --> 00:02:41,720
According to the calendar,

23
00:02:41,910 --> 00:02:44,710
it was a good day.

24
00:02:44,940 --> 00:02:46,250
I remember

25
00:02:46,560 --> 00:02:48,430
the solar term that day

26
00:02:48,430 --> 00:02:49,910
was Major Snow.

27
00:02:50,520 --> 00:02:54,590
Mother Nature really did
make it snow that day.

28
00:02:51,980 --> 00:03:00,490
[Ning Residence]

29
00:02:55,030 --> 00:02:56,280
That day

30
00:02:56,590 --> 00:02:59,520
was also my wedding day.

31
00:02:59,520 --> 00:03:02,280
Sister-in-law, can you help me
see if it's straight?

32
00:03:02,280 --> 00:03:03,250
It's straight.

33
00:03:03,280 --> 00:03:05,590
It's like this hairpin was made for you.

34
00:03:05,590 --> 00:03:07,050
My sister is so beautiful.

35
00:03:07,120 --> 00:03:07,910
Of course.

36
00:03:08,560 --> 00:03:10,030
She's like a city girl.

37
00:03:10,560 --> 00:03:12,630
The Fei family's ancestors
must've done great deeds

38
00:03:12,630 --> 00:03:15,000
to let Fei Wendian marry such a good wife.

39
00:03:15,000 --> 00:03:16,070
Xiuxiu!

40
00:03:21,840 --> 00:03:24,120
Xiuxiu, are you done?

41
00:03:24,590 --> 00:03:25,120
How is it?

42
00:03:27,310 --> 00:03:29,000
My daughter is so pretty.

43
00:03:31,800 --> 00:03:34,910
Mother, everyone says I look like you
when you were young.

44
00:03:34,910 --> 00:03:36,310
Do I look even more like you now?

45
00:03:36,310 --> 00:03:37,360
Who said that?

46
00:03:38,400 --> 00:03:40,060
You're much prettier than me.

47
00:03:41,470 --> 00:03:42,800
Just wait.

48
00:03:43,150 --> 00:03:44,079
In a while,

49
00:03:44,240 --> 00:03:45,590
in a few more hours,

50
00:03:46,030 --> 00:03:49,090
the Fei family will be here
to pick you up in their sedan.

51
00:03:50,550 --> 00:03:52,110
By the way, Lianye,

52
00:03:52,400 --> 00:03:54,310
have you prepared
the soup balls to be eaten

53
00:03:54,310 --> 00:03:55,520
before going on the sedan?

54
00:03:55,520 --> 00:03:57,400
It's still early. I'll do it later.

55
00:03:57,400 --> 00:03:58,360
Go now.

56
00:03:59,400 --> 00:03:59,910
Okay.

57
00:03:59,910 --> 00:04:01,800
Mother, let me taste it for Xiuxiu.

58
00:04:01,800 --> 00:04:02,470
Enough.

59
00:04:03,400 --> 00:04:04,930
You gravitate toward food.

60
00:04:05,120 --> 00:04:06,380
It's not your wedding.

61
00:04:07,130 --> 00:04:08,300
Close the door.

62
00:04:08,330 --> 00:04:09,490
Why?

63
00:04:13,910 --> 00:04:14,680
Xiuxiu.

64
00:04:15,560 --> 00:04:16,040
Here.

65
00:04:16,920 --> 00:04:18,320
This is ten silver coins.

66
00:04:19,070 --> 00:04:21,730
It's my personal savings,
not from your father.

67
00:04:22,680 --> 00:04:24,430
Although the Fei family is a rich family,

68
00:04:24,430 --> 00:04:26,360
it's better to have your own money.

69
00:04:26,630 --> 00:04:28,070
Your father didn't prepare any for you,

70
00:04:28,070 --> 00:04:29,480
but I can't let you down.

71
00:04:29,720 --> 00:04:30,070
Mother.

72
00:04:30,070 --> 00:04:31,310
Susu has it too.

73
00:04:31,390 --> 00:04:31,800
Here.

74
00:04:32,000 --> 00:04:32,950
-No.
-Be good.

75
00:04:32,950 --> 00:04:34,390
I have nowhere to spend it.

76
00:04:34,390 --> 00:04:34,920
Alright.

77
00:04:34,920 --> 00:04:36,270
Xiuxiu, just take it,

78
00:04:36,270 --> 00:04:37,510
or else Father'll ask for it back.

79
00:04:37,510 --> 00:04:38,190
Be good.

80
00:04:38,800 --> 00:04:39,310
Yes.

81
00:04:39,510 --> 00:04:40,600
Don't let your father know.

82
00:04:40,600 --> 00:04:42,190
Otherwise, he'll quarrel with me again.

83
00:04:42,190 --> 00:04:43,159
Thank you, Mother.

84
00:04:43,159 --> 00:04:45,560
