96
00:05:09,360 --> 00:05:10,430
I guess

97
00:05:11,000 --> 00:05:12,530
that Mrs. Fei

98
00:05:12,560 --> 00:05:14,560
is so anxious.

99
00:05:20,360 --> 00:05:20,950
Done.

100
00:05:22,070 --> 00:05:23,530
I've tested it all for you.

101
00:05:24,240 --> 00:05:24,800
Take it.

102
00:05:29,430 --> 00:05:30,160
Xiuxiu,

103
00:05:30,720 --> 00:05:32,270
I have a few words for you.

104
00:05:32,590 --> 00:05:33,390
Today,

105
00:05:33,760 --> 00:05:35,560
after walking through our door,

106
00:05:35,800 --> 00:05:36,750
you'll no longer be

107
00:05:36,750 --> 00:05:38,710
the eldest daughter of the Ning family.

108
00:05:38,710 --> 00:05:41,159
You'll be the Fei family's
daughter-in-law.

109
00:05:41,159 --> 00:05:42,960
Get married and live a good life.

110
00:05:43,480 --> 00:05:44,800
Learn from Mrs. Fei

111
00:05:44,920 --> 00:05:46,870
how to manage the family

112
00:05:47,720 --> 00:05:49,920
and respect her as your sister-in-law.

113
00:05:52,190 --> 00:05:52,830
Mother,

114
00:05:53,520 --> 00:05:54,690
you told me

115
00:05:55,070 --> 00:05:56,680
a sister-in-law is like a mother.

116
00:05:56,680 --> 00:05:58,480
I know the etiquette.

117
00:06:01,000 --> 00:06:02,530
Let me look at you some more.

118
00:06:04,180 --> 00:06:08,660
[Fei Residence]

119
00:06:09,830 --> 00:06:12,000
Dear ancestors of the Fei family,

120
00:06:12,510 --> 00:06:13,970
Father, Mother, husband,

121
00:06:15,120 --> 00:06:16,120
today

122
00:06:16,250 --> 00:06:19,500
