126
00:06:27,920 --> 00:06:29,830
I won't disappoint you all.

127
00:06:32,470 --> 00:06:33,750
After Wendian's wife

128
00:06:34,390 --> 00:06:36,600
bears children for the Fei family,

129
00:06:37,730 --> 00:06:39,240
I'll hand the Fei family

130
