[Memorial Tablets of the Ancestors
of the Fei Family]

131
00:06:39,830 --> 00:06:41,920
over to Wendian's hands.

132
00:06:58,630 --> 00:06:59,430
Madam!

133
00:07:00,190 --> 00:07:01,070
Madam!

134
00:07:01,780 --> 00:07:03,140
I'm back, Madam!

135
00:07:03,510 --> 00:07:04,770
You picked up Wendian?

136
00:07:05,190 --> 00:07:05,870
Madam,

137
00:07:05,970 --> 00:07:07,430
I went to the inn in the county.

138
00:07:07,430 --> 00:07:08,750
But the people there said

139
00:07:08,750 --> 00:07:10,240
Young Master left before dawn.

140
00:07:10,240 --> 00:07:11,190
I asked them where he went.

141
00:07:11,190 --> 00:07:12,590
They didn't know either.

142
00:07:14,670 --> 00:07:15,990
Where else can he go?

143
00:07:16,680 --> 00:07:19,080
He probably got impatient and walked back.

144
00:07:19,480 --> 00:07:21,240
Did you see him on your way back?

145
00:07:21,390 --> 00:07:22,160
No.

146
00:07:23,410 --> 00:07:24,850
Then he took a shortcut.

147
00:07:24,870 --> 00:07:25,990
It's snowing hard.

148
00:07:26,040 --> 00:07:27,700
Small paths aren't walkable.

149
00:07:28,070 --> 00:07:28,750
Quickly

150
00:07:28,750 --> 00:07:30,800
find some people who often work for us

151
00:07:30,800 --> 00:07:32,720
and search everywhere carefully.

152
00:07:32,720 --> 00:07:34,510
Search the snow nests too.

153
00:07:34,630 --> 00:07:35,190
Go now.

154
00:07:35,190 --> 00:07:36,450
Iâ€™ll get going, Madam.

155
00:07:39,680 --> 00:07:40,680
Two packets of wedding pastries

156
00:07:40,680 --> 00:07:42,070
from Li Suozhu's household.

157
00:07:42,070 --> 00:07:43,159
Hefty.

158
00:07:44,920 --> 00:07:45,680
Best wishes

159
00:07:45,870 --> 00:07:47,430
for Master and Madam!

160
00:07:49,120 --> 00:07:49,680
Let's go.

161
00:07:50,310 --> 00:07:51,310
This is yours?

162
00:07:54,600 --> 00:07:55,480
It's from me.

163
00:08:06,160 --> 00:08:07,160
One packet of wedding pastries

164
00:08:07,160 --> 00:08:08,480
from Feng Si's household.

165
00:08:08,480 --> 00:08:09,390
It's...

166
00:08:09,800 --> 00:08:10,630
quite a lot.

167
00:08:11,950 --> 00:08:12,920
Thank you.

168
00:08:13,630 --> 00:08:14,560
Thank you.

169
00:08:14,920 --> 00:08:17,180
I'm here to sincerely give my blessings.

170
00:08:18,000 --> 00:08:21,160
Can you lower some of my interest?

171
00:08:21,180 --> 00:08:22,180
What do you think?

172
00:08:39,409 --> 00:08:40,770
Feng Si.

173
00:08:41,360 --> 00:08:42,000
You're pulling tricks

174
00:08:42,000 --> 00:08:43,720
on me now?

175
00:08:43,720 --> 00:08:44,480
N-No.

176
00:08:44,630 --> 00:08:46,360
Kuangzi, go get the ledger.

177
00:08:46,550 --> 00:08:48,270
I'll settle everything

178
00:08:48,320 --> 00:08:48,910
Feng Si owes today.

179
00:08:48,910 --> 00:08:49,670
No, don't.

180
00:08:49,670 --> 00:08:52,000
If you canâ€™t settle it,
pay with your land.

181
00:08:52,600 --> 00:08:54,200
Master Ning, Master Ning!

182
00:08:54,360 --> 00:08:56,320
Master Ning, please be generous.

183
00:08:56,730 --> 00:08:59,450
Donâ€™t mind me. I mean well.

184
00:08:59,510 --> 00:09:00,550
Cut the crap.

185
00:09:00,920 --> 00:09:02,820
If you don't settle the debt today,

186
00:09:02,820 --> 00:09:05,150
don't blame me
for not leaving you a way out.

187
00:09:05,150 --> 00:09:06,270
No, no, no.

188
00:09:06,390 --> 00:09:06,970
Master Ning.

189
00:09:06,970 --> 00:09:08,290
You know

190
00:09:08,320 --> 00:09:11,050
I'm so poor that I only have
the clothes on my back.

191
00:09:11,240 --> 00:09:13,630
I had to pawn a hoe

192
00:09:14,120 --> 00:09:14,960
to afford

193
00:09:14,960 --> 00:09:16,750
half a box of wedding pastries.

194
00:09:16,750 --> 00:09:18,840
But the shop doesn't sell half-boxes!

195
00:09:18,840 --> 00:09:20,270
They sold me some crumbs.

196
00:09:20,840 --> 00:09:22,750
How could I give them to you?

197
00:09:22,750 --> 00:09:24,790
I just thought...

198
00:09:26,270 --> 00:09:27,670
I'll kill you!

199
00:09:32,660 --> 00:09:34,190
When your father was alive,

200
00:09:34,670 --> 00:09:36,200
your family

201
00:09:36,670 --> 00:09:38,150
didn't fare too badly.

202
00:09:38,670 --> 00:09:39,840
Look at you now.

203
00:09:40,790 --> 00:09:43,520
You can't even compare
with your brother Feng Er.

204
00:09:43,750 --> 00:09:45,750
And you're trying all these tricks.

205
00:09:46,790 --> 00:09:48,910
For the sake of my dead father,

206
00:09:49,370 --> 00:09:50,430
please forgive me.

207
00:09:50,960 --> 00:09:51,890
Please spare me.

208
00:09:52,550 --> 00:09:54,840
With interest, 15 silver dollars in total.

209
00:09:54,840 --> 00:09:56,100
Go back and prepare it.

210
00:09:58,000 --> 00:09:58,750
