It's embarrassing.

216
00:10:10,300 --> 00:10:12,010
Don't worry about this.

217
00:10:13,240 --> 00:10:15,870
How dare he lie to me on the wedding day?

218
00:10:17,400 --> 00:10:19,470
You know it's the wedding day?

219
00:10:19,750 --> 00:10:22,480
You should accumulate merits
for your daughter.

220
00:10:22,510 --> 00:10:23,200
Get up.

221
00:10:23,590 --> 00:10:24,200
Kneel.

222
00:10:26,600 --> 00:10:27,240
Kneel!

223
00:10:27,290 --> 00:10:28,820
Kuangzi, see the guest out.

224
00:10:29,520 --> 00:10:31,780
Kuangzi, everyone who comes is a guests.

225
00:10:31,790 --> 00:10:32,960
Make some tea.

226
00:10:32,960 --> 00:10:33,870
Bring the wedding pastries

227
00:10:33,870 --> 00:10:34,960
to host everyone.

228
00:10:34,960 --> 00:10:36,150
Okay, Madam.

229
00:10:36,580 --> 00:10:37,180
Get up.

230
00:10:41,170 --> 00:10:43,410
Madam, my whole family

231
00:10:43,440 --> 00:10:45,270
will never forget your kindness.

232
00:10:45,270 --> 00:10:46,180
Go. Go.

233
00:10:51,910 --> 00:10:53,120
Grandpa Ox,

234
00:10:54,060 --> 00:10:56,900
thank you for blessing
Ox Temple Village.

235
00:10:58,030 --> 00:10:59,630
Let me sweep the snow for you,

236
00:11:00,240 --> 00:11:01,150
so that

237
00:11:01,150 --> 00:11:02,350
you're more relaxed.

238
00:11:11,120 --> 00:11:12,400
Great snow!

239
00:11:15,440 --> 00:11:16,960
This year's wheat

240
00:11:17,630 --> 00:11:18,720
sleeps in the snow.

241
00:11:19,390 --> 00:11:21,510
Next year, I'll sleep with a bun.

242
00:11:23,440 --> 00:11:27,270
Threading and flour for your face.

243
00:11:27,840 --> 00:11:31,390
I'll eat your wedding pastries this year

244
00:11:32,080 --> 00:11:35,550
and your red eggs next year.

245
00:11:36,150 --> 00:11:40,000
Threading and flour for your face.

246
00:11:40,270 --> 00:11:42,030
I can't hide it from you.

247
00:11:44,080 --> 00:11:45,480
I feel

248
00:11:47,200 --> 00:11:48,270
so sad inside.

249
00:11:52,240 --> 00:11:54,360
I've liked Xiuxiu since childhood.

250
00:11:59,960 --> 00:12:02,030
But she's marrying Fei Wendian now.

251
00:12:23,510 --> 00:12:25,030
Go, go, go!

252
00:12:25,480 --> 00:12:26,600
What's wrong?

253
00:12:27,770 --> 00:12:29,100
Go away.

254
00:12:34,700 --> 00:12:36,910
