258
00:12:41,360 --> 00:12:42,890
Dung is created from grain.

259
00:12:43,200 --> 00:12:44,510
Grain births dung.

260
00:12:44,630 --> 00:12:45,830
You think it's dirty,

261
00:12:46,270 --> 00:12:49,130
but I think you poor people
don't understand at all.

262
00:12:49,670 --> 00:12:51,550
When you harvest more grain,

263
00:12:51,720 --> 00:12:54,120
