272
00:13:13,450 --> 00:13:15,850
I feel so humiliated.

273
00:13:18,540 --> 00:13:19,870
I came out today

274
00:13:19,870 --> 00:13:22,390
to make those forgetful people

275
00:13:22,620 --> 00:13:24,290
remember

276
00:13:24,390 --> 00:13:25,870
